 holo), Negros: Negros Occidental, Mt Dumalabdab, Talisay mun., 10°40'N, 123°16'E, hill forest, rocky clay, 1160m, 25-Mar-1992. Distribution: Endemic to the Philippines. NEGROS, PANAY (photos). Notes: Evergreen rainforest and grassland. Fl. & fr. Mar-Jun. 100m (photos) to 1160-1200m. Native. ssp. philippinensis. = Lobelia nicotianifolia var. mollis Elmer, LPB 9 (1934) 3180; Type: Elmer 22181 (PNH, holo, lost; MO, iso), Luzon: Pampanga, Camp Stotsenburg, Mt Pinatubo, May-1927. Distribution: Endemic to the Philippines. LUZON: Aurora, Benguet, Ifugao (photos), Ilocos Norte, Zambales. Notes: Forest openings. Fl. & fr. Oct-Apr. 500-1600m. Native.", "distribution": "Endemic to the Philippines. BILIRAN, CAMIGUIN, LUZON: Apayao (photos), Aurora, Benguet, Ifugao (photos), Ilocos Norte, Mountain Province, Zambales, MINDANAO: South Cotabato (photos), NEGROS, PANAY (photos).", "notes": "In Luzon from Ilocos Norte to Aurora to Zambales. Open spots on ridges in the mossy forest, often on grassy mountain slopes and hillsides. 100-1600m.", "conservation_status": "", "dao_category": "", "other_fields": {}, "gallery_url": "http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/cgi-bin/bhbase/cubic_gallery_public.pl?start_at=0&taxon_name=Lobelia+philippinensis", "thumbs": ["http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/CUBIC_IMAGES/phytoimages/pelserpb/3_31_09/32may09/LobeliaNicotianaefolia.jpg.400.jpg", "http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/CUBIC_IMAGES/phytoimages/pelserpb/3_31_09/32may09/LobeliaNicotianaefolia1.jpg.400.jpg", "http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/CUBIC_IMAGES/phytoimages/pelserpb/4_1_09/1apr09/LobeliaNicotianaefolia.jpg.400.jpg", "http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/CUBIC_IMAGES/phytoimages/pelserpb/4_1_09/1apr09/LobeliaNicotianaefolia1.jpg.400.jpg", "http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/CUBIC_IMAGES/phytoimages/pelserpb/6_8_11_1/8jun11a/Lobelianicotianaefolia.jpg.400.jpg", "http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/CUBIC_IMAGES/phytoimages/pelserpb/6_8_11_1/8jun11a/Lobelianicotianaefolia1.jpg.400.jpg", "http://herbarium.bh.cornel